@startuml
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
title BGM State Machine -- Semaphore-based Multi-layer Switching

state Normal : Normal BGM\ngame_bgm.ogg\nvolume=0.3
state Boss : Boss BGM\nboss_bgm.ogg\nvolume=0.5
state Invincible : Invincible SFX\ninvincible.ogg (loop)
state Cooldown : Cooldown 5min

[*] --> Normal : Game Start

Normal --> Boss : MusicState.set(1)\nEnter Boss area
Boss --> Normal : MusicState.reset()\nGame restart

Normal --> Invincible : SPACE activate\nStop normal BGM
Boss --> Invincible : SPACE activate\nStop boss BGM

Invincible --> Normal : 30s expire\nMusicState=0\nRestore normal BGM
Invincible --> Boss : 30s expire\nMusicState=1\nRestore boss BGM
Invincible --> Cooldown : -50% HP + energy=0

Cooldown --> Normal : 5min over
Cooldown --> Boss : 5min over

note right of Normal
  BUG 1: Boss killed, restart game
  => BGM not reset
  FIX: call MusicState.reset()
  in _restart_game()
end note

note right of Invincible
  BUG 2: After invincible ends
  => all audio lost
  FIX: stop() first, then
  load correct BGM by MusicState
end note
@enduml
